videos.headline: Notre Dame wins ACC Championship with late-game heroics
videos.description: Notre Dame's Sonia Citron comes down with a clutch rebound late in the fourth quarter to ice the game against NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Notre Dame wins ACC Championship with late-game heroics) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sonia Citron connects with nice pull-up jumper
videos.description: Notre Dame's Sonia Citron works around the screen and gets the shot to fall over her defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sonia Citron connects with nice pull-up jumper) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aziaha James sinks smooth step-back shot for NC State
videos.description: NC State's Aziaha James shows off her handles and crosses up her defender for a clean step-back jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aziaha James sinks smooth step-back shot for NC State) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hannah Hidalgo drains triple for Notre Dame
videos.description: Notre Dame's Hannah Hidalgo shows off her range and splashes home a 3-pointer against NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hannah Hidalgo drains triple for Notre Dame) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Madison Hayes nails trey vs. Notre Dame
videos.description: NC State's Madison Hayes finds herself open and doesn't miss from 3-point range against Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Madison Hayes nails trey vs. Notre Dame) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maddy Westbeld denies bucket with slick swat
videos.description: Notre Dame's Maddy Westbeld just gets enough to reject the shot and send it out of bounds against NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Maddy Westbeld denies bucket with slick swat) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: River Baldwin fights through contact for bucket
videos.description: NC State's River Baldwin won't be denied as she gets an impressive shot to drop against Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (River Baldwin fights through contact for bucket) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: NC State's Zoe Brooks slings behind-the-back dime
videos.description: Zoe Brooks gets flashy on the fast break with a behind-the-back assist to cut down on Notre Dame's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (NC State's Zoe Brooks slings behind-the-back dime) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maddy Westbeld gets the tough and-1 to fall
